from will_it_saturate.core import Benchmark
from will_it_saturate.server import FastAPIUvicornServer
from will_it_saturate.client import HttpxClient, AioHttpClient
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
byte = 8
gigabit = 10 ** 9
bandwidth = gigabit / byte

# file_sizes = [10 ** 7, 10 ** 6]
file_sizes = [10 ** 7, 10 ** 6, 10 ** 5]
# file_sizes = [10 ** 7]

server = FastAPIUvicornServer()
benchmark = Benchmark(
    bandwidth=bandwidth,
    duration=3,
    file_sizes=file_sizes,
    servers=[server],
    clients=[HttpxClient(name="httpx"), AioHttpClient(name="aiohttp")],
)
benchmark.create_rows()
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
%%time
benchmark.run()

measure
measure
measure
